data.description:
Welcome to 60 Hickory Lane, a beacon of down-home values and organic living, now for sale in the heart of Bloomfield, KY. This modern ranch, built in 2015 and set on a spacious 10-acre plot, offers a harmonious blend of comfort, sustainability, and freedom. With an open floor plan featuring four bedrooms and three bathrooms, this home is ideal for nurturing a family or embracing a peaceful, self-reliant life.

The property, equipped with Starlink Internet, provides the perfect balance between staying connected and living a serene, rural lifestyle. The expansive land is a blank canvas for organic farming, gardening, or small-scale agriculture, allowing you to grow your own food and live off the land in true Kentucky spirit.
